Package: ohm-plugin-core
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: OHM libraries and plugins
 This package contains libraries needed for running OHM and
 developing OHM plugins.

Package: ohm-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
